creator: Deltaee
descriptionHtml:
Wood block puzzle games meet a sudoku grid. It’s a calm but challenging puzzle that you’ll be addicted to in no time!

Place blocks in the 9x9 board and fill rows, columns or squares to clear them from the game. Play for as long as you can without running out of space to beat your high score!
Playing Sudoku 99 wood block puzzle game will be addictive! Keep challenging yourself to get higher scores! Playing Sudoku 99 block puzzle game may be time-consuming! It is not easy to break your own record. But hard work is fun! Adjust your strategy and continue to work hard!
If you like wood puzzles and elimination games, or Block Hexa puzzles or Woody Block Puzzle, then Sudoku 99 is the perfect choice for you. Immerse yourself in this brain game and escape from everyday anxiety and negative bad thoughts. You must not be bored! Use a relaxing and challenging Sudoku 99 game to release stress or train your brain, anytime, anywhere!

🍉How to Play:
✔ Drag shapes onto the board to place them in the grid.
✔ Fill a row, column, or square to clear blocks from the board.
✔ Clear multiple rows, regions, or squares to earn Combo points!
✔ Clear blocks on every turn to earn Streak points!
✔ Earn as many points as you can to beat your high score!
✔ Have yourself a woody good time!
🍉 More people are enjoying it
✔ Natural Wooden style theme brings you a Zen moment.
✔ Simple UI plus brisk sound effect.
✔ Pass daily challenges and achieve golden trophies.
✔ Play offline without data or WIFI. Relaxing gameplay with no time limits.
✔ Lightweight to install. 100% free wooden puzzle sudoku.

Sudoku Game with your friends and families! Have fun and exercise your brain with this Wood Sudoku 99!
From now on, let's enjoy a simple and addictive wood block puzzle game! Once you start, you'll be hooked!
You can play wood block puzzle anytime and anywhere!
We really hope you enjoy playing wood block puzzle!

A great wood block puzzle game help you relax and train your brain. This block puzzle game is unlimited style with many play modes, you can play as long as you want without being interrupted. Solve this block puzzle faster than anybody else and reach the first place on the leaderboard. It combines the wood block puzzle and sudoku! It is simple to play and fun to keep challenging yourself!

Place blocks in the 9x9 board and fill rows, columns or squares to clear them from the board. Play for as long as you can without running out of space to beat your high score! Relieve stress or train your brain with a simple yet challenging free block puzzle you won’t be able to put down. Keep the board clean and beat your high score in this block puzzle! Test your IQ and win the wood block puzzle game!

How to Play:
. Drag and drop blocks into 9×9 grid
. Fill the blocks with a row or column to eliminate them
. Game will be over if there is no room on the board for given blocks
. Reward scores for each step and every row or column of blocks you eliminated
More people are enjoying it
. Beautifully easy and simple, no pressure and no time limit.
. Boost your highest score to reach the top rank
. Forever free to play, easy to play
. Offline mode, no Wifi Needed!
. Daily bonus

Let's play this Wood sudoku: block puzzle game with your friends and families!
From now on, let's enjoy a simple and addictive wood block puzzle game! Once you start, you'll be hooked!
We really hope you enjoy playing this Block Puzzle Game anytime and anywhere!
